&lt;p>🔹 &lt;strong>Main Character:&lt;/strong> &lt;strong>Alice&lt;/strong> – a curious and imaginative young girl.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>🔹 &lt;strong>Plot:&lt;/strong> Alice follows a &lt;strong>White Rabbit&lt;/strong> down a rabbit hole and enters a bizarre world called &lt;strong>Wonderland&lt;/strong>, where nothing makes sense and logic is twisted. She meets &lt;strong>strange characters&lt;/strong>, faces &lt;strong>absurd challenges&lt;/strong>, and grows or shrinks in size after eating or drinking magical things.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>